{"word":"Leaven","slug":"leaven","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Leaven</b> For bread<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=34'>Exo 12:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=39'>Exo 12:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=4'>Hos 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=33'>Mat 13:33</a><br/> Leavened bread used:<br/> - With peace offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=13'>Lev 7:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=5'>Amo 4:5</a> <br/> - With wave offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=17'>Lev 23:17</a> <br/> Leavened bread forbidden:<br/> - With meat offerings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=11'>Lev 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=6&verse=17'>Lev 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=12'>Lev 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=18'>Exo 23:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=25'>Exo 34:25</a> <br/> - At the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=20'>Exo 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=4'>Exo 13:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=7'>Exo 13:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=18'>Exo 23:18</a> <br/> - With blood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=18'>Exo 23:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=25'>Exo 34:25</a> <br/> A type of sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Co 5:8</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Figurative:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=12'>Mat 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=15'>Mar 8:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=1'>Luk 12:1</a> <br/> - Of other evils<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=5&verse=8'>1Co 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=9'>Gal 5:9</a> <br/> - Parable of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=33'>Mat 13:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=21'>Luk 13:21</a> "}]}